# Cursor rules for Relia Intranet

The canonical context for this repo lives in `CLAUDE.md` at the root. Read it before suggesting any non-trivial change.

Key rules (full list in CLAUDE.md):
- Never commit secrets.
- Never bypass Supabase RLS. Service-role key is server-only.
- Migrations are append-only. Never edit a merged migration.
- Architectural choices require an ADR in `docs/decisions/`.
- Linear is the source of truth for work. Branch names: `REL-123-short-slug`.
- No `any` in TypeScript without a justifying comment.
- Tests for every new API route or server action (Vitest, co-located).

When suggesting code:
- Prefer server components for data fetching.
- Use `@/lib/supabase/server` for server-side Supabase client, `@/lib/supabase/client` for browser.
- For new agents or skills, add a markdown file under `docs/agents/` or `docs/skills/` and link it from `CLAUDE.md`.

When in doubt, open `CLAUDE.md` and the relevant `docs/decisions/*.md` files.
